            . I am clerk to Mr. Dver, who is a <rs id="t17740907-85-viclabel411" type="occupation">sugar-baker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17740907-85-victim671 t17740907-85-viclabel411"></join>; on the 15th of August I was at <placeName id="t17740907-85-crimeloc412">Ralph's-Key</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17740907-85-crimeloc412" type="placeName" value="Ralph's-Key"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17740907-85-crimeloc412" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17740907-85-off409 t17740907-85-crimeloc412"></join>; we had fifteen hogsheads of sugar there for shipping, and they were weighed; the coopers came down to hoop them; the prisoner is a <rs id="t17740907-85-deflabel413" type="occupation">cooper</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17740907-85-defend669 t17740907-85-deflabel413"></join>; I was informed the prisoner had taken some sugar out of the hogsheads; I weighed them over again, and found four of them plundered.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17740907-85-person673">
                  John
                   Dixon
               <interp inst="t17740907-85-person673" type="surname" value="Dixon"></interp>
